info on a command:
$man a_command

e.g.
$ man ls
grep:

grep [options] string filename

# search directory my_dir

grep string my_dir

# search current directory
grep string .


# to sort files by name
ls | sort -n 

# find differences between two files (other versions exist)
diff file_1 file_2

Uninstall Homebrew packages:

$ brew uninstall <name>


Dealing with and Removing Packages (Mac .pkg packages only):

List all packages:
$ pkgutil --pkgs

